    "stat_block": {
        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "Made of cobalt-colored steel rings that flow down the entire length of the garment, this *+1 resilient chain mail* includes an armored face covering. The armor is said to be based on the same armor once worn by Azure Leopard, one of Old-Mage Jatembe's magic warriors.",
