                    "effect": "You call upon the ferocity and grace of the leopard. The armor's rings flatten out to become a solid piece of flexible armor. You gain a +2 item bonus to Stealth checks and Intimidation checks to Demoralize, but take a \u20132 penalty to Diplomacy and Society checks. This lasts for 1 hour, but you can Activate the armor again to revert it back to its original form.",
